    "question_id" : 1444437,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>One nasty thing about Guava is that Multimap does not extend java.util.Map. If You have Your own methods that work on Maps they won't work on Guava Multimaps (Apache MultiMap interface does extend java.util.Map). I'm sure that there's some good reason why it's the way it's but it's also inconvenient.</p>\n"
